{
  "stem": "21527.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was my first lot of formal schooling since my kindergarten days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went to sixth grade because I was already 11 at that stage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we somehow settled into a more or less normal life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The anti-Semitism in Poland was just terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Poles resented that any Jew had survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Oh, you survived!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you look so well!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you're wearing a hat!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Like you had to apologize for, for still being alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We kept in touch with some of the inmates from the-- from the camp who also settled in Czestochowa after the war.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A lot of people came for advice, for a meal, for a kind word.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then one-- and then we made contact with my family here in Australia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Before we knew it, we had permits to come here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the decision wasn't easy because my uncle knew that he wouldn't be able to practice as a doctor in Australia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But then a pogrom took place in one of the city's not far from Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Actually, a few months ago there was a 50 year commemoration of this pogrom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that pogrom made my uncle and aunt decide that it was time to leave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That there was no future for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because not only had the Poles organized this pogrom, but to the Russians also very quietly supported it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So between the Russians and the Poles, we were really in a very precarious situation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And my uncle was frightened to go out on, on night calls because if somebody asked him to come to look to a sick person, it could've been a hoax.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So he was really not safe working in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So in July 1946, we packed up, and we left.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
